question:
Analyze the code. What is the output?

```java
class Box {
    int width;
    Box(int w) { width = w; }
}

class Test {
    static Box modify(Box b) {
        b.width *= 2;
        return b;
    }
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Box box = new Box(5);
        Box newBox = modify(box);
        System.out.print(box.width + " " + newBox.width);
    }
}
```
